# AVAudioVoiceProcessingSpeechActivityEvent.ended

**Case**

Indicates the end of speech activity.

## Declaration

```swift
case ended
```

## Events

- **AVAudioVoiceProcessingSpeechActivityEvent.started**: Indicates the start of speech activity.
